title: Police identify victim killed in fatal Kinloch shooting - KMOV.com
content:
KINLOCH (KMOV.com) -
Authorities are investigating a fatal shooting that occurred in Kinloch Thursday afternoon.
17-year-old Antoine Quinn was found fatally shot in the passenger seat of a car near the intersection of Monroe and Granberry around 3:20 p.m., police say. Nobody else was in the car.
Quinn had been shot several times.
Police are still searching for the suspect.
